'''Abxazya''' (s tutlayt tabxazit: Аҧсны, s tutlayt tajurjit: აფხაზეთი, s tarusit:Абха́зия) tga tamnaḍt mmaɣn fllas kra n tmizar tzga f uftas n ugmuḍ n yill asggan. Tbṛṛḥ azarug nns f Jurjya asggas 1991 dffir imnɣi gr Jurjya d Abxazya. Tga tagduda nna dar ur amyassan sdat tmizar n umaḍal ɣar zɣ Rusya d Nikaragwa d Finzwila d Nawru. Ɣ usggas 1993 umṛn isrdasn n jurjya f azggiz ɣ tamnaḍt dffir imnɣi isuln nig n usggas ,d igrawliyn inbḍawn.

Tiwḍ tajumma nns 8432 km², tamaẓunt nns Suxmi, zɣ tiɣrmin nns nniḍn tixatarin Bitswanda, Gali, d Gagra tbedd tdamsa nns f tmaṛṛayt , ar ttamẓ Abxazya f uzgn n iftasn n Jurjya izaykutn (Jurjya dat asggas 1989) ttbedd tdamsa n tmazirt n Abxazya f tkrza d ufars n ṭaba , illa dar Abxazya igran n ṭaba imqqurn lliɣ tga 37.4% n tjumma nns aman ibuɣla igr n tkrziwin imqqurn s ufars n lɣllat, lliɣ tbuɣla s unzwi ugris ɣ tgrst d anammas ɣ unbdu ibuɣla ufars n watay d ur igdal uya igllil n tdamsa n Abxazya acku ibidd f igran n usggas tḍḍar s imukrisn n unzwi d tdamsa d tsrtit anzwi n Abxazya ugris d illa f udrar d uya inqqa takrza.
